4. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The concept of network stability can be related to systems and control, and the proposed problem can be seen as a control problem of finding critical connections. 
5. cs.DB (Databases) - The paper deals with a social network and proposes a problem of finding critical connections, which can be related to database management.
